Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Master was as cute as always today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She truly is an angel from Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the door already! I'm in my boxers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the folks will be visiting\NMom's hometown over the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As of tomorrow, it'll be just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna get some food delivered?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A-and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go back home today,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it will just be me and my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so bad about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our house is Hell as it is, but now it will be Hades!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Hades different from Hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you should just stay here tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAAAAAAAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-i-i-is th-th-that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll have to ask my brother, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll head over to Bomba's place later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be lonely without you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You already knew about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah, he'd mentioned it at the Enoshima aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guess I'll make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So full...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite filling, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to Bomba's. I'll be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, about me being here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd rather I not say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right. I get the feeling\Nhe'd be worried otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,S-see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Master... your brother is kind, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindness like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It sort of reminds me of Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, let's play a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels a little strange being under someone else's roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's YOUR house like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty old and rundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our house, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck, Kirie? You're so late,\Nthat I was worried you'd gotten lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I took the long way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a piggyback ride! C'MON!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the Master is calling out to me while she's dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're riding a fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A fish?! Don't tell me she's\Nformed a bond with my storybook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, you're gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Master, I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kirie, I'm tellin' you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until the start of elementary school,\Nshe'd be all like, "Big Brother!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Taihei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah. I'm listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you? Are you listening? You gotta listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, my Kirie...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone off and made some great friends,\Nlike Tanukichi and Ebina, and I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Taihei? Well, Taihei?! Taihei!\NAre you listening? Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey! I am!\NAre you listening, Taihei? Well, Taihei?! Taihei!\NAre you listening? Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Taihei? Well, Taihei?! Taihei!\NAre you listening? Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,TAIHEI!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my... reading manga indoors on a hot day\Nwith the AC blasting sure is great, huh, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're ending it HERE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bet it'll follow the standard pattern of him\Nnot hearing over the sound of the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda vexing, but you want to root for them because\Na romantic comedy needs a happy ending, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Root for them...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, what's got you yelling all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that vision just now was my dark side...\Nand that was something I would've said up till recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like those two are a couple now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for our next girls' day out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you two start dating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of boy would you like to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru sure is cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a great bod, and she's smart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And good at sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Umaru"? That's MISS Umaru to you, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, what's got you crouching all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to admit that I just can't get used\Nto being part of a community.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All I would ever do is despise the people around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... made an enemy I must defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I... cannot root for love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure gets emotionally involved with her manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get that worked up about it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie wants to be a storybook author, so maybe\Nthat's why she's taking this manga so personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I must give her\Na definitive answer, as her Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to overthink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one thing is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you should just believe in what you want to believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What I... believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? You're in your school uniform ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something that I would ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You like Taihei Doma, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was obvious from your reactions the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I wish to discuss with you.\NI have decided on something this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to root for them because\Na romantic comedy needs a happy ending, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall root for your love with all my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just believe in what you want to believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I believe in... is my Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,O..okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My little sister, Umaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is renowned for her beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's kind and smart, and graced with many talents.\NShe's loved by young and old, men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's flawless, the perfect high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... that's what everyone seems to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Umaru when she's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My lazy, dried fish of a sister... a himouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,HEY! Get up, Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! What, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now look here, Umaru:\Nsummer vacation isn't just for lazing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a time for you to do and experience things\Nyou don't usually have the chance to at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, Big Brother.\NI may not look it, but I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I always read Jumpu, but today I got Jumpu SQUARE!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm not so sure what "Square"\Nis supposed to mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good. I have to at least get her outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru! There's a fireworks festival today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be lots of big, beautiful fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing is to try to get her\Nto an event that she'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, no thanks. There's too many people,\Nand insects, and it'll be hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I was thinking we could buy some food\Nfrom the stalls there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not buying all that! How greedy can you be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for sitting around! Let's go, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The festival's at NIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat the small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaruuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is a different person outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We should invite the others. Let's start with Ebina!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so she wanted to go with her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You invite Taihei to the fireworks festival.\NThat will create just the right mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,M..mood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great, isn't it, Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,N-n-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWe've already been to the beach together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei and Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hello, Umaru, Taihei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kirie. You're visiting Ebina, huh? Perfect timing.\NWhat do you say we all go to the fireworks festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The fireworks festival, you say? Of course I will go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad. Now we can all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come on in, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't want to go yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There are preparations to be made! And you too, Taihei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed! A fireworks festival\Nmeans one must wear a summer kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let us depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have a lot to learn, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the stalls!\NThe stalls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the stalls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall visit them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I get you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No, I can pay for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbababababa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shugaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's sit here and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an especially large star mine, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure make a lot of sound, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive fireworks, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look it, but I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We should invite the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My younger sister is a "himouto," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,while some things don't change,\Nlittle by little, some things do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get up, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,G'morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to go to school. Summer vacation's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't keep Ebina waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Do you have the day off today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, to make up for lost vacation time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... to go buy groceries, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Then buy some potato chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we shall all eat together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Umaru, the teacher was looking for you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To give you your certificate from that awards ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. It always takes a while\Nto actually get your award, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been on display in front\Nof the staff office this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the last time two people got awards\Nat the same time was 10 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? 10 years ago? That might have been my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he always had\Nthe top grades in his school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Bomba said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This brother and sister have some impressive specs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Your brother is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Umaru's brother, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This bread is cheap! Maybe I'll make cream stew today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he is SO kind-hearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought souvenirs and bought us\Nso many things at the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, he's kind\Nand makes you feel at ease somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That he does...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No, Ebina, I was just thinking,\NI'd like a brother like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to the principal's office,\Nso you all go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. See you later, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,U-until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei Doma sure was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Taihei the Demon," they called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Takes you back, doesn't it? He was an excellent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Umaru's brother, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And makes you feel at ease somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an excellent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's just come back from shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I'll scare him from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sure to give him a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Biiig Brothe-!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I think you've got the wrong person...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Umaru. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I feel like I've seen this girl somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, at the awards ceremony.\NShe's the girl from the AP class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. She's a friend of yours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, we go to the same school\Nbut I wouldn't say we're friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the outdoors... I want to go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:18:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You want to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, your name is Kongo, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you over today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time we've talked, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to keep up appearances,\Nso just lounge around as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! She knows about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei is always lounging around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Always lounging...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even talked to her before,\Nbut she's fixated on Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's way too mysterious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother is MY big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I do feel like I know her from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I heated up some bread. Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Umaru? Ah! You've eaten it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl ate it all! In, like, a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a little girl like this\Ncould eat THREE of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is! It's Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Kanau's younger sister, aren't you?\NYou sure have gotten bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You know her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember that girl\Nfrom when we went to Hamamatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my boss, Kanau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hikari is her younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a REALLY long time since I've seen her,\Nbut I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no no no! That's MY big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be okay? Do you want me to walk you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some cream stew that will be ready soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll come back again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:20:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,B-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hi to Kanau for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is! It's Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she call you "Big Brother"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure... she did used to call me that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she suddenly show up today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? To hang out with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never hung out with her! That girl's just fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It had been so long since I'd seen my big brother\Nand we were able to talk. I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! Like I said, he's MY big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're determined to call him that, though,\Nthen you can call me "Big Sis"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast!
